      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/martinruizn?tab=repositories"
          class="btn !text-neutral-900 dark:!text-neutral-900">Ver en GitHub</a
        >
        <a href="/blog" class="btn-outline !text-neutral-900 dark:!text-brand"
